Company



About Syniverse


Loading the player...

At Syniverse, we make mobile work. We empower mobile operators and other enterprises to deliver enhanced, reliable mobile experiences with any mobile user – anytime, anywhere.
We've been a mobile pioneer since the dawn of the industry, and today we connect more than 1,000 operators and more than 500 other enterprises in almost 200 countries. In particular, we specialize in bridging technology islands and commercial worlds so that our customers can reach, protect and engage their mobile users. From our position at the center of the mobile ecosystem, we simplify complexity to allow the world's mobile users to connect with each other regardless of device, network or location.
Syniverse enables mobile service providers to solve today's challenges of mobile connectivity and interoperability. Our product groups address the areas of connectivity, messaging, intelligent roaming, partner management, and fraud and revenue assurance, and they are centered around the concept of "real-time intelligence." 
At the same time, we empower consumer companies to connect to the power of the mobile. Our enterprise products for mobile engagement, mobile reach and mobile protection help companies realize their mobile potential with a range of voice, text-message, email, push-notification and social-media solutions.
Today's mobile ecosystem is complex and rapidly evolving. It requires an expert navigator to help providers and enterprises unlock value and deliver the mobile experiences that today's users demand. No matter the technology, the location or the provider, Syniverse makes mobile work.
Learn More




News
July 20, 2017

Syniverse Enables Cable & Wireless Seychelles to Improve LTE Roaming User Experience
Syniverse today announced that it has signed an agreement with Cable & Wireless Seychelles to help the operator improve roaming experiences for inbound and outbound roaming customers. The agreement builds on a multiyear relationship and marks another step in Cable & Wireless Seychelles’ ability to deliver the highest level of roaming experience and maximize revenues in a rapidly growing tourism market.
