Company Overview of Syniverse Holdings, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Syniverse Holdings, Inc. provides transaction processing and intelligence solutions enabling mobile communications for mobile network operators (MNOs), over-the-top providers (OTTs), and enterprises worldwide. The company offers mobile transaction services, including clearing, processing, and exchanging end-user billing records; processing and settling payments between participants in the mobile ecosystem; activating, authenticating, and authorizing of end-user mobile activities; managing the routing and delivery of SMS, MMS, and next generation messaging; data transport services; intelligent policy and charging tools; and risk management tools to prevent fraudulent activity on operator netw...
Syniverse Holdings, Inc. provides transaction processing and intelligence solutions enabling mobile communications for mobile network operators (MNOs), over-the-top providers (OTTs), and enterprises worldwide. The company offers mobile transaction services, including clearing, processing, and exchanging end-user billing records; processing and settling payments between participants in the mobile ecosystem; activating, authenticating, and authorizing of end-user mobile activities; managing the routing and delivery of SMS, MMS, and next generation messaging; data transport services; intelligent policy and charging tools; and risk management tools to prevent fraudulent activity on operator networks and identify problem areas in the end to end billing cycle. It also provides enterprise and intelligence solutions, such as connecting enterprises to the mobile ecosystem to reach and interact with their customers and employees through mobile devices; bridging OTTs to the mobile ecosystem allowing OTT end-users to interact with traditional mobile end-users; mobile communications initiatives; data analytics and business intelligence solutions; and solutions to enable MNOs to measure and manage the subscriber experience across networks. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Tampa, Florida. Syniverse Holdings, Inc. is a subsidiary of Buccaneer Holdings, LLC.
